cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.NE, cs.CV, cs.SI 

The paper deals with the application of deep learning techniques (LSTMs and attention mechanisms) for forecasting financial time series. This falls under the broad category of machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The use of neural networks for time series forecasting also falls under the category of neural networks (cs.NE). The paper also mentions the use of attention mechanisms for image processing, which falls under computer vision (cs.CV). Finally, the paper discusses the potential issues with such model architectures, which falls under the category of systems and control (cs.SI).
